<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="gesture-v">gesture <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'dʒestʃə(r)/    美 /'dʒestʃər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>做手势；用手势示意：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>"I see you read a lot," he said, <strong>gesturing towards / at</strong> the wall of books.
“看来你看了很多书，”他指着那一大摞书说。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He <strong>gestured to us that</strong> it was time to go.
他示意我们该走了。</p></div></div>